By":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhow-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg&h=3e7b9d93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2970eb771a136c7c3f5d3bde3a2da62ee5a49c84","tid":406153,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成吉思汗同俄羅斯有咩關係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打死哂原有強大國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俄羅斯擴張既主要方向係西伯利亞本身有咩強大國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身15世紀俄莫斯科大公國最大既敵人就是蒙古人諸汗國同諾夫羅斯夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7d9884be8acecb61c09df9afefcdc240d1d02d","tid":406153,"uid":138790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯人擴張要分亞洲部分同歐洲部分<br />\n亞洲靠火槍,哥薩克騎兵同梭堡,利用農業帝國國力優勢殖民消滅遊牧汗國,再由西伯利亞運皮革去西歐賣,殖民西伯利亞<br />\n歐洲主要靠彼得大帝西化,打敗北歐霸主瑞典成功搶佔波羅的海出海口,後面強敵波蘭同奧斯曼衰落再向佢地擴張<br />\n拿破崙之後就向中亞同英國搶地"},{"pid":"3da50b3d29546b201a85312b14df87523e43a15e","tid":406153,"uid":138790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhow-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg&h=3e7b9d93&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n無美英援助 蘇聯42年應該無資源打落去被迫講和/投降"},{"pid":"f15ff61d8655fa63dda40513f785106dbcfd9e41","tid":406153,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好間接地可以話關嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但整體俄羅斯人都係好憎蒙古人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為蒙古人對當時既俄羅斯地區造成嘅破壞實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係好多俄羅斯貴族<br />\n甚至沙皇<br />\n都有蒙古血統<br />\n包括著名嘅彼德大帝"},{"pid":"6a90de761009b227c565b3dcd93a8a0d3e478b43","tid":406153,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhow-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg&h=3e7b9d93&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n無美英援助 蘇聯42年應該無資源打落去被迫講和/投降</blockquote><br />\n打完基輔包圍戰<br />\n根本全世界都認為蘇聯仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76c1f83c8524d55ce448e5c53070fbc2cb77763","tid":406153,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好間接地可以話關嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但整體俄羅斯人都係好憎蒙古人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為蒙古人對當時既俄羅斯地區造成嘅破壞實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係好多俄羅斯貴族<br />\n甚至沙皇<br />\n都有蒙古血統<br />\n包括著名嘅彼德大帝</blockquote><br />\n咁蒙古人同俄羅斯人擴張有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ac92df3b0833f51ef5ef650f4d4c6bb2a40eed","tid":406153,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhow-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg&h=3e7b9d93&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n無美英援助 蘇聯42年應該無資源打落去被迫講和/投降</blockquote><br />\n打完基輔包圍戰<br />\n根本全世界都認為蘇聯仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以美英同蘇聯一結盟馬上賣身家咁輸血比蘇聯,怕佢比德三打死"},{"pid":"8c15d6f9802e02786bb53ed2db6fede5cbb2dd31","tid":406153,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"彼得大帝?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%9D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BD%25BC%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%259D&d=w88n7XjJPWrSIIDKLyujaSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b58aa14e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%9D</a>"},{"pid":"ffacfc5e43d33389ba713b37868cc58057f7b316","tid":406153,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhow-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg&h=3e7b9d93&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d52abb3f610e75659166f4df93720e2418d79ad","tid":406153,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-w