lockquote><br />\n一戰法國打到無曬底氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國比意大利好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d20e6248330bb2bb01495a878b42ca304dcd0db","tid":406153,"uid":76756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhow-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg&h=3e7b9d93&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一戰法國打到無曬底氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國比意大利好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be46621743a7df9c4af06f27ac27b1400434750c","tid":406153,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"有d地方日温差成50度以上<br />\n揾鬼住咩"},{"pid":"b4f91dc3ff354bad239ce82e5c024f4726e9daa8","tid":406153,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好間接地可以話關嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但整體俄羅斯人都係好憎蒙古人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為蒙古人對當時既俄羅斯地區造成嘅破壞實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最少都有開拓左俄仔既地圖知識"},{"pid":"afb118fe860fdeb9c19e560090aa597d8f15f3fb","tid":406153,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好間接地可以話關嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但整體俄羅斯人都係好憎蒙古人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為蒙古人對當時既俄羅斯地區造成嘅破壞實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係好多俄羅斯貴族<br />\n甚至沙皇<br />\n都有蒙古血統<br />\n包括著名嘅彼德大帝</blockquote><br />\n咁蒙古人同俄羅斯人擴張有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遺傳咗兵制同對外擴張嘅基因"},{"pid":"6bf73221c7e5674d1543e05b6ab02ab0c112e5ab","tid":406153,"uid":56287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>彼得大帝?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%9D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BD%25BC%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%259D&d=w88n7XjJPWrSIIDKLyujaSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b58aa14e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%9D</a></blockquote><br />\n沙皇家族有蒙古血統，伊凡四世的母親椰列娜是成吉思汗的直系後裔，一&shy;直到彼得大帝 臉上還有明顯的蒙古特徵，列寧有卡爾梅蒙古血統。蒙古韃靼人不僅把血統形式傳給了俄羅斯人，而且把政治制度，稅收制度，海關制度和軍事制度也傳給了俄羅斯人，蒙古人為俄羅&shy;斯貢獻了鮑裏斯和費德爾戈杜諾夫兩位沙皇。六位皇后：所羅門尼婭?薩布洛娃；椰列娜?格林斯卡 娃；伊琳娜?戈杜諾娃；納塔利婭?納雷什金娜馬爾法?阿普拉克希娜；葉夫多基婭?薩布羅娃。"},{"pid":"3bef558ba09b86fd9c757d1e0484c8f50d51e389","tid":406153,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/how-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhow-people-think-world-war-2-was-how-it-really-was-ww2-explained-on-dinosaurs.jpg&h=3e7b9d93&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一戰法國打到無曬底氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n駁唔到，蘇聯要收返俄羅斯帝國東歐失地同附屬國<br />\n德國要搭搶東歐物資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國發現蘇聯開始搶埋中歐先識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瘋狂登陸西歐，最後先保得住半個德國同法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}